# theta

Extensions for multithreaded Python applications.

## Install

```sh
pip install theta-alkasm
```

## Development

In a virtual environment:

```
$ poetry install
$ poetry check
$ poetry run pytest
$ poetry run black theta
$ poetry run mypy theta
```

